= System Dependencies

Ths command requires the following common system tools:

* Bash 3.2 or higher
* Git 1.7.0 or higher
* `curl`

At this stage, it probably will only work on a POSIX system (ie not Windows).

= Configuration

The LW API needs to know your user name and password for your Liquid Web
account. You'll need to use the `lw config` command to set these.

